Death watched as his prey fell to the ground. Sparks flying from his 
neck..."You are not worthy of this group. And your evil and treachery has 
come back to haunt you." he split is reaper in two and through them down so 
to hold both of his arms in place at the ground. "Death  takes your spark to 
HADES!!" he took the spear frombehind his back and drove it at Phobia's chest.
